================================================================================
WHAT THIS IS
================================================================================

A derivative summary of publicly published frameworks, organized as a
configuration file for Claude Code (https://claude.com/claude-code) so an
AI assistant can apply those frameworks during personal coaching sessions
for the copyright holder.

It is not a substitute for:
  - Reading "The Great CEO Within" by Matt Mochary
  - Hiring a Mochary Method coach
  - Reading the original source materials linked in SKILL.md and NOTICE.md
  - Professional legal, medical, psychological, or financial advice

