================================================================================
FAIR USE STATEMENT
================================================================================

This repository constitutes a transformative summary of publicly
available educational materials, organized for a specific
non-commercial purpose: enabling an AI assistant to apply publicly
published CEO coaching frameworks during personal coaching
conversations with anyone who installs the skill. It is the position
of the copyright holder that this constitutes fair use under 17 U.S.C.
§ 107 (United States) and analogous doctrines in other jurisdictions,
considering:

  1. Purpose and character: non-commercial, educational, transformative
     (reformatted for a new use case — AI-assisted personal coaching —
     not a substitute for the source works).
  2. Nature of the original work: publicly published, openly distributed
     educational material that the original author Matt Mochary has
     explicitly invited people to learn from and apply, with the express
     goal of spreading the methodology.
  3. Amount used: frameworks are paraphrased and synthesized; no
     copyrighted book (including "The Great CEO Within") is reproduced
     verbatim or in substantial part. Only short framework names and
     concepts — none of which are individually copyrightable as ideas —
     are reused, each with attribution.
  4. Market effect: this work drives users TOWARD the original (book
     purchases, coach hiring at mocharymethod.com), not away from it.
     This is reinforced throughout README.md, NOTICE.md, and SKILL.md.

This statement is the copyright holder's position and is not a
determination of law. Disputes will be addressed in good faith under
the takedown provision above.
